Summary: shape-shifting, round or oblong, metallic no wings or propellers
divs: sighting detailsi was driving west on parmer lane around 8:15 - 8:30 a.m., i saw a round object that seemed to be floating, but heading north\north east. it did seem to control it's own destination. at one point it turned and appeared to have a red metallic color. i called my husband but by the time he could get outside and see the object, it was so far away it just looked like a little black dot.
